## 🔵 Low — Naming & Structural Issues

- **All test names end in `_Works`** — gives zero diagnostic value when a test fails. Use `AddProduct_RoundTripsViaGet`, `UpdatePrice_ChangesStoredPrice`, etc.
- **Tests use a concrete `InMemoryStore`** instead of a mock, coupling unit tests to a second production class. A bug in `InMemoryStore` masks or creates false failures in `ProductCatalog` tests.

